              ></picture><span class="post--meta"><em class="post--meta-date">March 13, 2018</em><em class="post--meta-author">Jenna Simeonov</em><em class="post--meta-category">Interview</em></span></a><p class="post--list-desc">&quot;He is a super-genius who has created an invention that will change life as we know it. He is in obsessive love with Faustine. He has invited Faustine and the remaining characters (in the opera) to the island to woo Faustine. His gambit is to spend the rest of his days with her. ...which is kinda creepy on any level.&quot;</p><a href="/a-futuristic-love-story-the-invention-of-morel/" class="btn post--button">Read More</a></li><li><a href="/transfixing-soundstreams-presents-tan-duns-water-passion/" class="post--list-title"><h1>Transfixing: Soundstreams presents Tan Dun&#39;s Water Passion</h1></a><a href="/transfixing-soundstreams-presents-tan-duns-water-passion/" class="post--list-image"><picture><!-- <source srcset="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/rvulI6sB4BNxGbOf0gz7k7fIT9iC-M_vMB9A3sy7_5cnknIE0p7OdmrE56qTiNre99Bm1rMnXctrhIYOjnXuV84ALIjM=w680-h480-c 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/rvulI6sB4BNxGbOf0gz7k7fIT9iC-M_vMB9A3sy7_5cnknIE0p7OdmrE56qTiNre99Bm1rMnXctrhIYOjnXuV84ALIjM=w1360-h960-c 2x" media="(min-width: 40em)"> --><img
