              data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2DfHGdkJ3HogrfiBbNvOvfVtOt2eRmDfifdr87mE1qv7JB7Ae56OssJOitjHcSupp6c7DAZHzqQxNPWeSncrS7g1B1298g=w400-h300-c" alt="Levine&#39;s ugly exit, &amp; the disposable Met"
              data-srcset="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2DfHGdkJ3HogrfiBbNvOvfVtOt2eRmDfifdr87mE1qv7JB7Ae56OssJOitjHcSupp6c7DAZHzqQxNPWeSncrS7g1B1298g=w680-h480-c 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2DfHGdkJ3HogrfiBbNvOvfVtOt2eRmDfifdr87mE1qv7JB7Ae56OssJOitjHcSupp6c7DAZHzqQxNPWeSncrS7g1B1298g=w1360-h960-c 2x" alt="Levine&#39;s ugly exit, &amp; the disposable Met"
              ></picture><span class="post--meta"><em class="post--meta-date">March 13, 2018</em><em class="post--meta-author">Jenna Simeonov</em><em class="post--meta-category">Editorial</em></span></a><p class="post--list-desc">Now, as I read the conclusion of the Met&#39;s gross display of Righteous Responseâ„¢ - their investigation, launched with seriousness only after this group of victims came forward with corroborating, damning accounts of abuse by Levine - I say, let it fall.</p><a href="/levines-ugly-exit-the-disposable-met/" class="btn post--button">Read More</a></li><li><a href="/kyra-millan-making-opera-for-all-ages/" class="post--list-title"><h1>Kyra Millan: making Opera for All Ages</h1></a><a href="/kyra-millan-making-opera-for-all-ages/" class="post--list-image"><picture><!-- <source srcset="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/lbqnj3In1EJBgTRG9O1g_db6sevrSv1rCQ-7247JRabnLwRkYqEXp7TApNZChWjBt-M8UMPOpmwmBGI0G8YtMKgM8dop_A=w680-h480-c 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/lbqnj3In1EJBgTRG9O1g_db6sevrSv1rCQ-7247JRabnLwRkYqEXp7TApNZChWjBt-M8UMPOpmwmBGI0G8YtMKgM8dop_A=w1360-h960-c 2x" media="(min-width: 40em)"> --><img
